item.title: A14X Apple TV 6 - You want GOOD News or BAD News First?!
item.description:
The Apple TV 6 has been rumored for a LONG time, and now we're finally getting closer to its release. Let's discuss some fresh leaks and rumors.. including some BAD News as well.. Best Game Controller for Apple TV ➡ https://geni.us/e1ly7
A14 Bionic Leaked Benchmarks ➡ https://youtu.be/W1r_fzvQLmo FULL Apple Silicon Macs Explained Playlist ➡ https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLo11Rczpzuj05que94HF80LWD217ToJht How Gaming will work on Apple Silicon Macs ➡ https://youtu.be/XOFEwWKPsxo Why Apple Silicon ARM Macs will NOT have discrete GPUs! ➡ https://youtu.be/BMs_-bZBqxg
In this video, I show you guys a bunch of leaks about the Apple TV 6, including Apple's upcoming game controller.
I discuss the history of Apple TV Leaks and rumors, and then I get into the fresh leaks that help give us a release date and more info on what to expect.
